{"tid":103450,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿 嬌 認 有 用 iCloud：我 d相 無 乜 野 既","createTime":"2017-02-01T10:45:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-04T17:02:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50690b2c16dd9fbd754abb90fe4743f15e2984ea","tid":103450,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:45:15.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=7f766acc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】 鍾欣潼出席澳門活動，說到荷里活女星的私密裸照，被黒客入侵iCloud而被盜取放到成人網站一事，阿嬌大方說有使用iCloud，她謂：「我啲相冇乜嘢嘅，咁因為都好方便，啲相會自動上載上去。」 <br />\n問到是否替一班荷里活女星不值？阿嬌坦言：「我覺得呢樣係好私人嘅事，大家偷睇咗人哋嘅嘢仲要鬧人唔啱！其實都唔係佢哋自願公開畀人睇，偷睇完仲反而鬧人哋，咁唔係好唔啱咩？」而阿嬌直言沒有看這些女星裸照：「有冇美感都唔應該睇。」 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20140902/photo/bkn-20140902185031570-0902_00862_001_06b.jpg?193727?t=1409668913409\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20140902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20140902185031570-0902_00862_001_06b.jpg%3F193727%3Ft%3D1409668913409&h=bf6843d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"664fb189368cbde72852d5326eeaa87633fc47a3","tid":103450,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T10:45:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20140902/photo/bkn-20140902185031570-0902_00862_001_03b.jpg?193727?t=1409668931715\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20140902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20140902185031570-0902_00862_001_03b.jpg%3F193727%3Ft%3D1409668931715&h=1ba0aea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿嬌語重心長話大家唔應該睇完啲相仲鬧人！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xW6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=7f766acc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a><br />\n東網娛樂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/ent/20140